      "content": "it's not about a \"next chapter.\" that's the thing. i don't think there is one. i feel like i've reached the edge of the world and there's just nothingness beyond it. like, if i just stepped off the path and let the journey end here, wouldn't that be a kind of peace? a way to finally be still?",
